4 P's of marketing and 4 C's of marketing

Product affects customer benefits

Brand communities:
  customer brond from commond brand purchases. 
  Video game companies and such that gain a fan base.

Co-creation:
  customer participate in the design or production process of the brand.
  Lays offering a customer to choose one of their flavors
  
Crowdsourcing: 
  The use of individual or groups outside the organization to provide assistance
  Basically like a gofundme 
  Waze uses this since people report traffic conditions and the app tells others about it

Gamification:
  Using games to interact with customers, to amke the interaction better
  Mcdonalds monopoly

